Enum Rarity

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Rarity>, java.lang.constant.Constable
    public enum Rarity
extends java.lang.Enum<Rarity>
    Possible rarities of different cards.

    Decks typically can only have two or fewer of all rarities, and one or fewer of LEGENDARY cards.

    These rarities affect some effects, like CardFilter, which can select cards of a specific rarity; the draft logic in the net module; and the gem that appears in the middle of the card.
